about.summary: A Python module that implements the jinja2.Markup string

name: markupsafe
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.23" %}

package:
  name: markupsafe
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: MarkupSafe-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/M/MarkupSafe/MarkupSafe-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: f5ab3deee4c37cd6a922fb81e730da6e

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - markupsafe

about:
  home: http://github.com/mitsuhiko/markupsafe
  license: BSD 3-clause
  summary: A Python module that implements the jinja2.Markup string

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pelson
